CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 27, 1963, pg. 9 reads: "Contestants - The Greater Pittsburgh Elks Lodge and Ruth Temple 116 are co-sponsoring a contest to select "Miss Elk of '63'."  All of the contestants are associate members of the Greater Pittsburgh Lodge 115.  First row (left to right): Arlene Hardy, Catherine Jones and Annabyrd Campbell.  Standing: Audry Tolliver, Carrie Brown, Mary Ann Harper and Hortense Palmer. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of seven contestants for "Miss Elk of '63'," sponsored by Greater Pittsburgh Elks Lodge 115,  from left: seated: Arlene Hardy, Catherine Jones, and Annabyrd Campbell; standing: Audry Tolliver, Carrie Brown, Mary Ann Harper, and Hortense Palmer posed around sofa with striped back cushions in interior, horizontal format
